      Initialization hook for Analysis.getResult(). All result types should be appended with a neutral value using Analysis.<T>append(org.variantsync.diffdetective.analysis.AnalysisResult.ResultKey<T>,T). No other side effects should be performed during this methods as it might be called an arbitrary amount of times.
